{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3637 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3637 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3637","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'function' : a friend function definition cannot be a specialization of a function type","pos":[618,705]},{"content":"A friend function was defined incorrectly for a template or generic.","pos":[712,780]},{"content":"The following sample generates C3637:","pos":[787,824]},{"content":"Possible resolution:","pos":[955,975]},{"content":"C3637 can also occur when using generics:","pos":[1113,1154]},{"content":"Possible resolution:","pos":[1314,1334]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3637 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3637\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3637\"\nms.assetid: 72391377-8519-43d9-870a-73a6423deb74\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3637\n'function' : a friend function definition cannot be a specialization of a function type  \n  \n A friend function was defined incorrectly for a template or generic.  \n  \n The following sample generates C3637:  \n  \n```  \n// C3637.cpp  \ntemplate <class T>  \nvoid f();  \n  \nstruct S {  \n   friend void f<int>() {}   // C3637  \n};  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C3637b.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \ntemplate <class T>  \nvoid f();  \n  \nstruct S {  \n   friend void f() {}  \n};  \n```  \n  \n C3637 can also occur when using generics:  \n  \n```  \n// C3637c.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr  \n  \ngeneric <class T>  \nvoid gf();  \n  \nstruct S {  \n   friend void gf<int>() {}   // C3637  \n};  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C3637d.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr /c  \ngeneric <class T>  \nvoid gf();  \n  \nstruct S {  \n   friend void gf() {}  \n};  \n```"}